features.text:
About Ex On The Beach: Couples

Six couples ready to get engaged must finally deal with their exes in a series of intense challenges before they decide if they want to finally commit to each other -- or cut ties for good.

collectible.name: Fine Dining Table (Black with Gold Trim)
collectible.description: This luxurious ebony wood dining table features a black table cloth with gold trim. Every fine establishment should have these tables for their patrons. Perfect for fine dining, ballrooms and event centers. Designed by Marsha McFly.

collectible.name: Fine Dining Chair (Black with Gold Accents)
collectible.description: This fancy black chair with gold accents perfectly complements the ebony wood fine dining table with black table cloth. Perfect for fine dining, ballrooms, and event centers.  This chair can also be used as a barstool. Designed by Marsha McFly.
